<div class="container" data-info="not-lightsail">

	<div class="head-about">
		<h1 class="about-h1">Nathan Broslawsky</h1>
		<p class="lead about-lead">{&nbsp;Engineering Leader, Polymath, Optimist&nbsp;}</p>
		<div class="leading-sweep">
			<p class="leading-sweep-intro">For motorcyclists, "Riding Sweep" means being the last bike on a group ride. The sweep ensures everyone else on the ride arrives at their destination safely.</p>
			<p class="leading-sweep-body">These same principles and philosophies carry forward into  leadership and the way I choose to coach and mentor others. <em>Being the sweep</em> means letting others take the lead, having your team's back, and remaining handy with a wrench if needed. <strong>Leading Sweep</strong> is a collection of articles diving deeper into how to grow and lead teams and other leaders in the same spirit.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="masonry isotopeContainer">

			{{#each homeStories}}
			<div class="col-md-4 masonry-row col-sm-6" data-url="{{preview.url}}">
				<div class="masonry-inner-container">
					{{#if preview.image}}
					<a href="{{preview.url}}"><img src="{{preview.image}}" alt=""></a>
					{{!-- <img src="{{preview.image}}" alt=""> --}}
					{{else}}
					<a href="{{preview.url}}" class="medium-date">
						<div class="medium-date-day">{{view.date}}</div>
						<div class="medium-date-month">{{view.month}}, {{view.year}}</div>
					</a>
					{{/if}}
					
					<div class="masonry-content">
						<a href="{{preview.url}}">{{name}}</a>
						<p class="spot ellipsis-readmore">{{preview.sanitized}} <a href="{{preview.url}}" class="more">Â»</a></p>
						<div class="links">
							<span>{{view.fulldate}}</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			{{/each}}

		</div>
	</div>
</div>


